~ no_watering_can
Plant: The plant looks dry and withered. It could really use some water.
=> END

~ has_watering_can
Plant: The plant looks dry and withered. It could really use some water.
Plant:
- Water the plant
	set GlobalDialoguesState.PuzzlePlant_Choice = 1
	Plant: You water the plant. It looks much healthier now!
- Cancel
	set GlobalDialoguesState.PuzzlePlant_Choice = 0
=> END

~ already_watered
Plant: The plant looks vibrant.
=> END
